Simulated Survey Data for Shape World

shape_survey.Rd

This is a simulated survey of whether Shape World voters prefer the Box Party (BP) or the Circle Party (CP) in the 2020 election. The data also include several demographic variables and the party the respondent voted for in the previous election. We use this data throughout the documentation to demonstrate the usage of the package.

shape_survey

Format

A data frame with columns:

age

Age group

gender

Gender

vote_for

Party voted for in the 2016 election

highest_educ

Highest grade of education completed

state

State

y

Preference for BP over CP in 2020 election

wt

Raked and trimmed survey weight

Source

Created in ShapeWorldVoters.R

Examples


 shape_survey
